<small_val> is a number:
    valid values:
        0 ... 10

<large_source> is a number:
    valid values:
        10 ... 20

<plan> is a plan:
    during plan:
        (* Error: [10, 20] is not subset of [0, 10] *)
        <small_val> = <large_source>.
        
        (* Error: 5 + 10 = 15. [15, 15] is not subset of [0, 10] *)
        <small_val> = 5 + 10.
        
        (* Error: Potential negative *)
        <small_val> = 5 - 10.
